The remote will have an LCD screen and speech recognition.
The advanced functions such as audio settings , contrast and channel programming will be accessed through the screen.
The target group will be aged 16-40.
A teletext option will not be included.
The remote will be for TV only.
The remote will feature the corporate logo and colour.
The screen and microphone will be at the top of the remote.
There will be LEDs under the buttons so that buttons in use will light up.
